revision.revdescription:
                    Calling qmr(A, Ap) is deprecated. qmr(A) should be used instead. The following function is an example :

function y = A ( x, t )
Amat = eye(2,2);
if ( t== "notransp") then
y = Amat*x;
elseif (t == "transp") then
y = Amat'*x;
end
endfunction
